A 10-count criminal indictment alleges that Michael Jackson and co-conspirators planned to abduct a child, falsely imprison someone, and extort another.
The son of Marlon Brando was implicated in a plot to kidnap the boy who accused Jackson of child molestation.
Amidst a feud with Eminem, Jackson's fans protested a music video depicting him in a controversial manner.
Facing child molestation charges, Jackson's trial is set for January 31.
Legal battles over unpaid bills and breach of contract add to the pop star's woes.
